{"tid":1757360,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"［黑店］Hair.royale salon","createTime":"2019-11-26T13:06:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-29T06:25:17.000Z","uid":147699,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"74e6bb31cc9b45a3eafc4f50d2bfab72f9e98e64","tid":1757360,"uid":147699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T13:06:56.000Z","msg":"首先講間鋪係極污糟，張枱好多頭髮碎同笠痴痴<br />\n我做染髮同整莉花頭，睇色板揀咗淺啡色，俾張佢地fb嘅相問可唔可以做，答做唔到一樣效果，但會差唔多，但最後變左mk橙啡色。<br />\n洗頭洗到我一面都係水，洗完又坐咗好耐冇人理....<br />\n個莉花頭電到一pat屎咁...變咗有啲內彎有啲外彎，佢仲話冇問題<br />\n剪髮，我話後面想剪薄，前面整空氣瀏海，但佢剪完變咗雜草，完全唔係空氣劉海，後面剪到一忽忽<br />\n重點係個態度....極臭串又是是但但，完全冇心幫你整靚<br />\n同埋大部份人都有食煙，真係接受唔到佢隻臭手掂我個頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n地址：旺角彌敦道726號21樓"},{"pid":"05f3ed62cf9420c43747a4c3595a47448920c56c","tid":1757360,"uid":147699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T13:25:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aaa15a6802f7c3e886ba65784444edd9c78c5040","tid":1757360,"uid":92401,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T13:45:59.000Z","msg":"冇相你話剪到葉劉咁都得啦"},{"pid":"2d6c51835db835e5a34729b8ff347e06643b9566","tid":1757360,"uid":125858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T04:32:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"678c9780ef92115d1dd857267e398c4862e1c06d","tid":1757360,"uid":284842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T04:22:02.000Z","msg":"點解會揀呢間呢，同埋你比佢張相睇係點樣架？"},{"pid":"79302190a0d978dbed5a93c26a28abf22ddb4d94","tid":1757360,"uid":283318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T06:25:17.000Z","msg":"樓主係即興去剪？<br />\ngoogle評分 1.4/5 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}